{"id":221234,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/windows-7中pptp、l2tp-vpn客户端的设置/","date":"2012-04-18T23:16:02Z","modified":"2012-08-31T22:12:05Z","title":"Windows 7中PPTP协议 VPN客户端的设置","content":"<p>VPN为Virtual Private Network的缩写，即虚拟专用网络，是一种常用于连接中、大型企业或团体与团体间的私人网络的通讯方法。VPN的信息通过互联网来传送内联网的网络信息）。VPN利用加密通道协议（Tunneling Protocol）来达到保密、客户端认证、信息准确性等私人信息安全效果，可以用不安全的网络来传送可靠、安全的信息。</p>\n<p>PPTP和L2TP是两种常用的VPN传输协议，本文主要介绍在Windows7中采用PPTP协议的VPN客户端设置方法。</p>\n<p><strong>1、选择 控制面板 -&gt; 网络和 Internet -&gt; 网络和共享中心</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2、单击设立一个新的连接或网络选项。</strong> <img style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 640px; width: auto; display: block; float: none; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" src=\"http://www.maizidi.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/10030.png\" alt=\"\" /> <strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong>3、向下滚动到列表的底部，并选择连接到工作场所，然后单击下一步。</strong> <img style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 640px; width: auto; display: block; float: none; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" src=\"http://www.maizidi.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/10031.png\" alt=\"\" /> <strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong>4、选择使用我的Internet 连接选项。</strong> <img style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 640px; width: auto; display: block; float: none; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" src=\"http://www.maizidi.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/10032.png\" alt=\"\" /> <strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong>5、在Internet地址栏，填入vpn服务器地址（即Caonima.net）；目标名称栏，可以随意输入一个容易区分的名称，比如CDT VPN。单击下一步。</strong> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/4-1.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-249691 aligncenter\" title=\"4-1\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/4-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/4-1.png 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/4-1-300x237.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a> <strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong>6. 输入账号及密码，点击“连接”，然后就可以使用VPN服务了。同样登陆<a style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline; color: #743399; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" href=\"http://www.ip138.com/\">http://www.ip138.com/</a>，看看你的ip变了没有？</strong> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/5-1.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-249692 aligncenter\" title=\"5-1\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/5-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/5-1.png 400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/5-1-300x237.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>参考资料： 1. <a style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline; color: #743399; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vpn\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vpn\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vpn</a></p>\n<p>版权声明：本站原创文章可以任意转载，请务必完整保留以下版权信息： <strong>转载自<a style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline; color: #743399; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" href=\"http://www.maizidi.com/\">麦子地</a> 链接地址: <a style=\"background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; border-image: initial; vertical-align: baseline; color: #743399; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\" href=\"http://www.maizidi.com/howto-configure-windows-xp-win7-pptp-l2tp-client/\">Windows XP和Windows 7中PPTP、L2TP VPN客户端的设置</a></strong></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[15300],"tags":[7775,8510,8795,8817]}